short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows you to open a GitHub repository on GitHub.dev

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can easily open any GitHub repository directly on GitHub.dev. Simply click on the extension button while you are on any GitHub repository page, and it will instantly take you to the editable version on GitHub.dev. Maximize your development workflow with this indispensable tool for GitHub developers.
